Package: masreml
Title: Universal REML-BLUP for SNP and Microhaplotype Genomic Prediction
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Wibowo", "Agus", email = "aguswibowo1698@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements BLUP, GBLUP, and PBLUP for genomic prediction using
    SNP (additive, dominance) and microhaplotype (additive) markers via
    V-based AI-REML with adaptive algorithm switching. Rust backend via extendr.
